      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides an overview of a novel approach to network layer packet forwarding, called tag switching.  The two main components of the tag switching architecture - forwarding and control - are described.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
